data.text:
Japanese Princess Akiko of Mikasa, elder daughter of Prince Tomohito of Mikasa and Princess Tomohito of Mikasa (Nobuko), visits the 71st Kanto Tokai Flower Exhibition in Toshima Ward, Tokyo on January 27, 2023. Hideaki Omura, Governor of Aichi Prefecture, visits too.( The Yomiuri Shimbun via AP Images )
